Class ADMService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.penthera.virtuososdk.client.subscriptions.ADMService
  • public class ADMService extends java.lang.Object
    This class allows your app to receive messages sent via ADM.

    You only need to create a subclass if you want to receive notifications of registration token changes and errors. To ensure the SDK continues functioning correctly always call super on the ADMMessageHandlerBase interface.
